quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  26,53,Waza uFir’awn wathumela ezixekweni abaqokeleli
  26,54,"(Wathi), Inene, bona aba baliqelana elincinane"
  26,55,Inene bona basenza umsindo
  26,56,Kanti thina siluluntu olunobubele.”
  26,57,Sabasusa ke ezitiyeni nasemithonjeni
  26,58,Nakoovimba nezikhundla ezihloniphekileyo
  26,59,Ngolo hlobo ke Senza aBantwana bakwaSirayeli ukuba babe ziindlalifa
  26,60,Babaleqa ke ukuphuma kwelanga
  26,61,"Kwathi imikhosi leyo mibini ukubonana kwayo, abalandeli bakaMûsâ bathi: “Inene thina siza kufunyanwa.”"
  26,62,"(UMûsâ) wathi: “Nakanye! Inene, iNkosi yam Ikunye nam. Iya kundikhokela Yona.”"
  26,63,"Satyhila kuMûsâ (Sathi): “Betha ulwandle ngomsimelelo wakho,” Lwahlukana kubini, icala ngalinye laba ngathi yintaba ephakamileyo"
  26,64,Saza Sabasondeza kufutshane abanye (umkhosi kaFir’awn)
  26,65,Samsindisa ke uMûsâ ndawonye nabo babekunye naye
  26,66,Sabatshonisa abanye (umkhosi kaFir’awn)
  26,67,Inene kule nto kwakungumqondiso kodwa uninzi lwabo babengazi kuba ngamakholwa
  26,68,"Kananjalo iNkosi yakho NguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  26,69,Kananjalo bacengcelezele ibali likaIbrâhîm (uAbraham)